name: Guanacaste by Matt Cipollone
description:
This modern scene of the iconic surfer in front of the huge wave creates a sense of proportional which so little photos have now a days. This combined with the black and white style creates a brilliant and individual shot.

name: Longstone Lighthouse by Cyan Aperture
description:
This unique photo is of Lonstone Lighthouse, off the Farne Islands.The contrast of a brewing storm and tranquil inlet waters creates a unique capture of the Northern Sea.  


 Laminated canvas prints offer 200 year UV protection, water resistance, cleanable and scratch/crack proof protection. Using 38mm deep European pine and real wood wedged corners we can offer perfectly tensioned canvas prints to admire. The frame also comes with felt to protect your walls. Canvas hanger fitted comes as standard.

The size of this piece is 36 inches by 12 inches. 

All canvases come bubbled wrapped and boxed. 

Please allow a little longer for delivery due to the size of the Canvas.

To buy this piece or just check out the rest of Cyan's portfolio visit:
